{
  "page": "House Sunderland",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the ironborn family, see <a href=\"/index.php/House_Sunderly\" title=\"House Sunderly\">House Sunderly</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Sunderland of the Three Sisters</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Sunderland.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Sunderland.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/250px-House_Sunderland.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/375px-House_Sunderland.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/500px-House_Sunderland.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nThree women's heads, white with black hair, on blue and green undy<br />(<i>Barry wavy azure and vert, three women's heads argents, crined sable</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sweetsister\" title=\"Sweetsister\">Sweetsister</a> <small>(possibly)</small><sup id=\"cite_ref-Jacaerys_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Jacaerys-3\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Triston_Sunderland\" title=\"Triston Sunderland\">Triston Sunderland</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Lord of the Three Sisters\">Lord of the Three Sisters</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Three_Sisters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Three Sisters\">King of the Three Sisters</a> <small>(historical)</small></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Vassals</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Borrell\" title=\"House Borrell\"><img alt=\"House Borrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/20px-House_Borrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/30px-House_Borrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/40px-House_Borrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Borrell\" title=\"House Borrell\">House Borrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Longthorpe\" title=\"House Longthorpe\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Longthorpe\" title=\"House Longthorpe\">House Longthorpe</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Torrent\" title=\"House Torrent\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Torrent\" title=\"House Torrent\">House Torrent</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Sunderland of the Three Sisters</b> rules the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a>, islands located in the <a href=\"/index.php/Bite\" title=\"Bite\">Bite</a>. The Sunderlands are sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>House Sunderland blazons their arms with three women's heads, white with black hair, on barry wavy blue and green.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> Their motto does not appear in the books. The name of their seat, possibly located in <a href=\"/index.php/Sweetsister\" title=\"Sweetsister\">Sweetsister</a>, is as yet unknown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Jacaerys_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Jacaerys-3\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#House_Sunderland_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Sunderland at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Historical_Members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Historical Members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Sworn_Houses\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Sworn Houses</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">the Conquest</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon the Conqueror</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a> rebelled against <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn_(king)\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn (king)\">Ronnel Arryn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" title=\"King of Mountain and Vale\">King of Mountain and Vale</a>, and named as their queen <a href=\"/index.php/Marla_Sunderland\" title=\"Marla Sunderland\">Marla Sunderland</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> flew on <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a> to end the <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Sistermen&#39;s Rebellion\">Sistermen's Rebellion</a>, however. The Sistermen deposed Marla, and her brother, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Sunderland\" title=\"Steffon Sunderland\">Steffon Sunderland</a>, submitted to King Aegon I.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jacaerys_Velaryon\" title=\"Jacaerys Velaryon\">Jacaerys Velaryon</a> flew on <a href=\"/index.php/Vermax\" title=\"Vermax\">Vermax</a> to Sisterton, where he received obeisance from Lords Sunderland and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Borrell\" title=\"House Borrell\">Borrell</a>. Jacaerys gained the Three Sisters for the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Sunderland\" title=\"Lord Sunderland\">Lord Sunderland</a> led the Sistermen fighting for <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackfyre\" title=\"House Blackfyre\">House Blackfyre</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"First Blackfyre Rebellion\">First Blackfyre Rebellion</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196&#160;AC</a>. He attended the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_tourney_at_Whitewalls\" title=\"Wedding tourney at Whitewalls\">wedding tourney at Whitewalls</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212&#160;AC</a> that was to launch the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"Second Blackfyre Rebellion\">Second Blackfyre Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Triston_Sunderland\" title=\"Triston Sunderland\">Triston Sunderland</a> is recalled by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Godric_Borrell\" title=\"Godric Borrell\">Godric Borrell</a> as having bemoaned the high cost of purchasing destriers for his seven sons, all of whom are determined to become <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Three of Triston's sons travel to the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a> to participate in the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_of_Winged_Knights\" title=\"Brotherhood of Winged Knights\">Brotherhood of Winged Knights</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Sunderland_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Sunderland at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Sunderland at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The only known Sunderlands during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Triston_Sunderland\" title=\"Triston Sunderland\">Triston Sunderland</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Lord of the Three Sisters\">Lord of the Three Sisters</a>.\n<ul><li>His seven sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical_Members\">Historical Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Historical Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Marla_Sunderland\" title=\"Marla Sunderland\">Marla Sunderland</a>, who ruled briefly during the <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Sistermen&#39;s Rebellion\">Sistermen's Rebellion</a> before being deposed by her own people.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Sunderland\" title=\"Steffon Sunderland\">Steffon Sunderland</a>, her younger brother, who succeeded her as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Lord of the Three Sisters\">Lord of the Three Sisters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li>Steffon's two sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li></ul></li>\n<li>Lord Sunderland, ruling during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Sunderland\" title=\"Lord Sunderland\">Lord Sunderland</a>, who participated in the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"First Blackfyre Rebellion\">First Blackfyre Rebellion</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_tourney_at_Whitewalls\" title=\"Wedding tourney at Whitewalls\">wedding tourney at Whitewalls</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Sworn_Houses\">Sworn Houses</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Sworn Houses\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"plainlist\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Borrell\" title=\"House Borrell\"><img alt=\"House Borrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/32px-House_Borrell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/48px-House_Borrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/64px-House_Borrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Borrell\" title=\"House Borrell\">House Borrell</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweetsister\" title=\"Sweetsister\">Sweetsister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Longthorpe\" title=\"House Longthorpe\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Longthorpe\" title=\"House Longthorpe\">House Longthorpe</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Longsister\" title=\"Longsister\">Longsister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Torrent\" title=\"House Torrent\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Torrent\" title=\"House Torrent\">House Torrent</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Littlesister\" title=\"Littlesister\">Littlesister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Jacaerys-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Jacaerys_3-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Jacaerys_3-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i> states that Jacaerys Velaryon called upon \"Lord Borrell and Lord Sunderland of Sisterton\",<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> but the more recent and comprehensive <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> states that Jacaerys \"lighted briefly at Sisterton, where Lord Borrell and Lord Sunderland did obeisance to him.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> This seems to imply that Lord Sunderland, ruler of all the Three Sisters, resided in Sisterton, or at least in Sweetsister; nevertheless, it is also possible Lord Sunderland may have traveled to Sisterton from Longsister or Littlesister for the meeting with the prince.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - A Son for a Son.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">3.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\">3.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\">3.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\">3.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\">4.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=